snippet.title: 'Justice for Johnny Depp' trends as ex-wife Amber Heard begins filming for 'Aquaman 2' | Cobrapost
snippet.description:
@Cobrapost JusticeForJohnnyDepp is back to topping worldwide social media trends after it was announced that production on Amber Heard's 'Aquaman and The Lost Kingdom' has begun.
Angry fans and netizen took to social media to slam the film's production house for keeping Heard as part of the superhero star-cast, while opting to remove Depp from the third part of the 'Fantastic Beasts' franchise, following his libel case. 
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp
